            <h1>OS Types (Intro)</h1>
            <div class="main-area">
                <div class="main-area-left"></div>
                <div class="main-area-center">
                    <p>Operating systems can be classified into different types based on how they manage tasks, users, and system resources.<br>
                        Each type is designed for specific environments such as personal computers, servers, or embedded systems.</p>
                    <img src="img/os-types.png" alt="OS Types">
                    <p>Below are four major types of operating systems commonly studied in computer science.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="main-area-right">
                    <a href="#batch" class="scroll-circle" aria-label="Scroll to next section">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="scroll-icon" aria-hidden="true">
