                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="batch" class="second-section">
            <h1>Batch & Time-Sharing Operating Systems</h1>
            <div class="main-area">
                <div class="main-area-left"></div>
                <div class="main-area-center">
                    <h2 class="bigger-font">Batch Operating System</h2>
                    <p>A Batch OS processes groups of jobs together without user interaction during execution.</p>
                    <h3>Characteristics:</h3>
                    <ul class="no-margin">
                        <li>Jobs are collected and executed in batches</li>
                        <li>No direct user interaction</li>
                        <li>Efficient for repetitive tasks</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Example: </strong>Payroll systems and large data processing systems.</p>
                    <h2 class="bigger-font">Time-Sharing Operating System</h2>
                    <p>A Time-Sharing OS allows multiple users or programs to share the CPU by dividing time into small slices.</p>
                    <h3>Characteristics:</h3>
                    <ul class="no-margin">
                        <li>Supports multitasking</li>
                        <li>Interactive</li>
                        <li>Quick response time</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Example: </strong>Unix and modern desktop operating systems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="main-area-right">

                    <!-- Go to Top (Double Up Arrow) -->
